is unrestricted funding for their general

00:52:20.329 --> 00:52:21.769
operating budget.

00:52:21.769 --> 00:52:25.940
What's your, what kind of advice do you give
to donors to get them to understand the importance

00:52:25.940 --> 00:52:26.940
